results.name: Triangle T(n,k) in which n-th row gives degrees of irreducible representations of symmetric group S_n. (cf. A060240) but now rows are sorted as indicated in A059797 with p(n) entries on each row, where p(n) = A000041(n).
comment: These are Betti numbers [Dochtermann]. - _N. J. A. Sloane_, Dec 02 2015
Number of entries on each row is A000041(n).
link: A. Dochtermann, Face rings of cycles, associahedra, and standard Young tableaux, arXiv preprint arXiv:1503.06243, 2015
example: A059797 begins 2 5 5 9 16 9 so row six of this sequence begins 1 5 10 10 5 1 9 16 9 ...
results.author: _Alford Arnold_, Mar 04 2002
